► What is SkyBlock Stranded?

Stranded is a new mode where players stay on their own island forever.

The rules are as follow:

-   Solo or Co-op.
-   Ironman rules.
-   You cannot leave your island.

The primary goal of Stranded is to unlock all the collections, but since most of them are not available directly from your island in Hypixel SkyBlock, many new mechanics were added to Stranded to implement them all.

We won't explain all the changes, but here are the largest ones:

-   Fishing Sea Creatures is available on your island.
-   There is a new icon inside the SkyBlock menu that lets you spawn specific SkyBlock NPCs anywhere you want.
-   If you can obtain Villagers, they have a custom trading system.

All the SkyBlock collections are currently available, except Mithril and Hard Stone, but no more spoilers. You'll have to figure out how to obtain the other collections through Jerry!
